text.paragraph:
Aripiprazole tablets are contraindicated in patients with a history of a hypersensitivity reaction to aripiprazole. Reactions have ranged from pruritus/urticaria to anaphylaxis [see 
                           Adverse Reactions (6.2)
                        ].

list.item:
Cerebrovascular Adverse Events, Including Stroke [see 
                              Warnings and Precautions (5.2)
                           ]
